1232
00:54:13,759 --> 00:54:15,010
Oh, Pops.

1233
00:54:15,803 --> 00:54:17,304
I wish it was over.

1234
00:54:18,138 --> 00:54:19,681
It will be soon, darling.

1235
00:54:21,433 --> 00:54:24,603
I'm sure that when you hold
your baby in your arms,

1236
