the next two or three weeks.

1245
00:54:52,506 --> 00:54:53,465
Two or three weeks?

1246
00:54:53,590 --> 00:54:56,260
I couldn't live like this
another two or three weeks.

1247
00:55:00,806 --> 00:55:01,682
Hello.

1248
