the baby's born by then.

1262
00:55:42,139 --> 00:55:43,724
Stanley, please hurry.

1263
00:56:00,741 --> 00:56:01,950
What kept you?

1264
00:56:02,075 --> 00:56:04,620
I'm just getting dressed.
I had to get my clothes on.

1265
00:56:04,745 --> 00:56:06,288
- I'll drive.
- Oh, no, no. Here, come on.

1266
00:56:06,413 --> 00:56:07,789
If we don't hurry,
the baby will be born

1267
00:56:07,915 --> 00:56:09,666
before we get there.
Come on.

1268
00:56:09,791 --> 00:56:11,543
The baby will be born,
and we'll never get there

1269
00:56:11,668 --> 00:56:12,711
