1270
00:56:24,056 --> 00:56:25,641
Don't go so fast, Ellie.

1271
00:56:25,766 --> 00:56:27,559
We're in a business district.

1272
00:56:32,856 --> 00:56:35,233
Ellie, slow down a little bit.

1273
00:56:35,359 --> 00:56:37,152
Uh-uh! Uh...

1274
