Ellie, for heaven's sake.

1275
00:56:40,948 --> 00:56:42,282
I had the right of way.

1276
00:56:42,407 --> 00:56:43,575
Keep your eye on the road.

1277
00:56:43,700 --> 00:56:45,827
Your tie's on crooked.
