1295
00:57:59,651 --> 00:58:02,863
Oh, that's alright.
Nothing at all, nothing at all.

1296
00:58:02,988 --> 00:58:04,823
- Good night, darling.
- Good night.

1297
00:58:04,948 --> 00:58:06,742
- Good night, Kay.
- Good night.

1298
00:58:06,867 --> 00:58:08,076
I'm sorry.

1299
