It's already here.
It's a boy.

1308
00:59:13,809 --> 00:59:16,061
He arrived
just half an hour ago.

1309
00:59:16,186 --> 00:59:17,979
Huh, okay, he's fine.

1310
00:59:18,105 --> 00:59:20,607
The doctor says
everything's just fine.

1311
00:59:20,732 --> 00:59:21,650
Yeah.

1312
00:59:21,775 --> 00:59:23,485
That's wonderful.

1313
00:59:23,610 --> 00:59:24,945
Wonderful.

1314
