Give her our love.

1315
00:59:27,697 --> 00:59:29,157
Give her our love.

1316
00:59:31,118 --> 00:59:32,077
Ellie.

1317
00:59:33,161 --> 00:59:34,454
- Ellie.
- Hmm?

1318
00:59:34,579 --> 00:59:36,289
Remind me to tell you
something in the morning.

1319
