1349
01:01:25,398 --> 01:01:27,192
- Perfect.
- Look at him!

1350
01:01:27,317 --> 01:01:29,736
Did you ever see
anything so good?

1351
01:01:29,861 --> 01:01:32,656
Did'ums have'um picture taken?

1352
01:01:32,781 --> 01:01:34,115
When is he going to
be christened?

1353
01:01:34,241 --> 01:01:35,283
In five or six months.

1354
