Take him, please.
Please, take him.

1375
01:02:23,039 --> 01:02:25,208
Oh, what's the matter?

1376
01:02:25,333 --> 01:02:27,002
My goodness.

1377
01:02:27,127 --> 01:02:28,586
Stanley, what'd you do to him?

1378
01:02:28,712 --> 01:02:31,589
What do you mean?
I didn't do anything to him.

1379
01:02:31,715 --> 01:02:34,634
I think he's tired.
We really must go.

1380
01:02:34,759 --> 01:02:38,054
By the way, Stan,
I had this made up for you.

1381
01:02:38,179 --> 01:02:39,973
It's a photographic
record of the baby

1382
01:02:40,098 --> 01:02:41,433
