1383
01:02:41,558 --> 01:02:42,809
Here, look at him here.

1384
01:02:42,934 --> 01:02:46,021
And then wait, wait.
Take a look at that.

1385
01:02:46,146 --> 01:02:47,647
And here, here.

1386
01:02:47,772 --> 01:02:50,442
Isn't it amazing?
Well, he changes every day.

1387
01:02:50,567 --> 01:02:51,901
Not to me, he doesn't.

1388
01:02:52,027 --> 01:02:54,321
- Coming, dearest?
- Here, put it in your pocket.

1389
01:02:54,446 --> 01:02:55,780
Show the boys, you know.

1390
01:02:57,115 --> 01:02:58,491
- Goodbye, dear.
- Good bye.

1391
